text: haey trong nung phdal leaphosakkar dl ke daoy ke nukasman min dl . haey anaknea del brakl kar touk chetd leu a l laoh ku trong chea anak phdal pheap krobkrean dl ke . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh kuchea anak sa me r ch nouv real kolbamnng robsa trong . pit nasa a l laoh ban bangkeut real avei teangoasa ku mean kamrit
